{
  "stem": "449.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I made a little money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Other jobs that were not enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As I said, the HIAS took care of us, and it was a very hard life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What were things like in the prison?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was easier in prison-- it was easier to take than in the hotel room where my wife with the-- for instance, we had no heat-- cold.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no way to make warm water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The baby was still one year old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a little burner with alcohol.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The alcohol doesn't even-- it took such a long time until a pot with water to make it warm, to wash the kid and to wash the diapers.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then when she hung up the diapers in the evening, in the morning when she needed it, it was frozen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was frozen in the-- This woman, what she went through, and always smiling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Always smiling and not complaining.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A heroine, really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was that terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was no comparison to what her sisters went through in the German concentration camp, but what she went through, and always smiling.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, she was left alone with the two kids, and I went to prison, knowing that prisons-- prison-- I never had it-- we had it very good there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What do you want, we had-- there was a concentration of German culture, German-Jewish culture.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were actors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were men of law, men of religion-- rabbis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were-- we had lectures.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had a university there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Lectures.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had theater, actors, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was unbelievable, the cultural life in the prison camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "3,000.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were also the German legionnaires, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
